46
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:23,340
The point is

47
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,820
the hub transfer contract is legit—

48
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,380
the provincial forensics

49
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,260
