50
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:30,690
And we have witnesses

51
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,610
saying Zhang coached someone to lie

52
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:34,220
to protect Wan Hai.

53
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,410
Plus the testimonies

54
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,290
from Wang Yu and others.

