he won't stir up trouble again?

172
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:35,700
The hub's evidence
in an active investigation.

173
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:36,980
The transfer can't happen

174
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:38,130
until Wan Hai is sentenced.

175
00:08:38,270 --> 00:08:39,250
It's yours for now,

176
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:40,580
all profits go to you.

177
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,650
You know how much trouble
Mr. Chen went through for this?

178
00:08:42,790 --> 00:08:44,820
Then see this through to the end!

179
00:08:45,030 --> 00:08:45,820
You know how long I've waited for this?

180
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:48,010
Three years.

181
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,610
Haven't I done everything

182
00:08:49,630 --> 00:08:50,820
