215
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,130
Why don't you

216
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:11,650
ask Mr. Chen to work something out.

217
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:15,300
I'll release Wan Hai's boy

218
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,420
