00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,940
the municipal bureau to correct it.

305
00:13:59,750 --> 00:14:01,850
Technical error, huh?

306
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:03,180
Zhang Wenjing's life

307
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:05,180
is ruined

308
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:06,940
