428
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:05,490
Now he's gone,

429
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,090
cremated

430
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:10,420
before I had a chance

431
00:19:10,750 --> 00:19:12,180
to say goodbye.

432
00:19:14,030 --> 00:19:15,290
By mistake, for god's sake.

433
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:17,180
It broke me.

434
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:19,570
I lashed out at everyone.

435
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:21,050
I just needed to let it out somewhere,

436
00:19:21,070 --> 00:19:22,380
