438
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:24,900
I lost it...

439
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,530
No need to explain.

440
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:26,530
Hong Liang,

441
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:29,250
